```

---

**Documentation**: [https://mrthearman.github.io/drf-tree-router/](https://mrthearman.github.io/drf-tree-router/)

**Source Code**: [https://github.com/MrThearMan/drf-tree-router/](https://github.com/MrThearMan/drf-tree-router/)

